  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Two new Non-Executive Directors appointed to the Student Loans Company Board
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Rona Ruthen and Gary Page appointed as Non-Executive Directors of the Student Loans Company </p>

  </div>
</div>

